# RoxyAPI key (required for the free readings) - get one at https://roxyapi.com/pricing
# Server side only. It is read by the server when a visitor requests a reading and never
# reaches the browser. The site builds and every page works without it; the reading pages
# simply say they are not connected yet.
ROXYAPI_KEY=your_roxyapi_key_here

# This is the only secret the project uses. Everything else a practitioner sets, including the
# publishable Web3Forms access key, lives in src/config/site.config.ts.
